
'''The Gods must be Crazy''' ni film yo gusetsa yo mu 1980 yanditswe, yakozwe, itunganywa kandi iyobowe na Jamie Uys . ubufatanyabikorwa mpuzamahanga muri Afrika yepfo na Botswana, ni film yambere muri '''The Gods must be Crazy''' series .

Iyi filime yashyizwe muri Afurika y'Epfo, ikinamo umuhinzi wo muri Namibiya San Nǃxau ǂToma nka Xi, umuhigi-uhiga mu butayu bwa Kalahari umuryango we wavumbuye icupa ry'ikirahure ryamanutse mu ndege, kandi bizera ko ari impano yatanzwe n'imana zabo. Igihe Xi yiyemeje gusubiza icupa ku mana, urugendo rwe ruba ruhujwe n’umuhanga mu binyabuzima (wakinnye nka Marius Weyers ), umwarimu w’ishuri ry’umudugudu mushya ( Sandra Prinsloo ), hamwe n’itsinda ry’iterabwoba .

'''''The Gods must be Crazy'''''  yarekuwe na Ster-Kinekor muri Afrika yepfo, aho yakoze amateka yinjiza amafaranga menshi, ikaba yarasohoye amafaranga menshi mumateka yinganda za firime za Afrika yepfo.  Iyi filime yagenze neza mu bucuruzi no mu bindi bihugu, harimo na Leta zunze ubumwe z’Amerika, aho yatanzwe na 20 Century Fox, aho ibiganiro [[Ikinyafurikansi|by’umwimerere bya Afrikaans]] yashyizwe mu cyongereza. Nubwo byagenze neza, iyi filime yakunze kunengwa kwerekana ubwoko kandi bigaragara ko atazi ivangura  muri Afurika yepfo. 

Film yakurikiwe ni ikindi gice  '''The Gods must be Crazy''' part II  yashyizwe ahagaragara Columbia Pictures mu 1989.

=== Gufata amashusho ===
''The Gods Must Be Crazy yafatiwe amashusho'' i Tsumkwe, muri Namibiya,  ndetse no muri Botswana.  

Nk’uko Uys abitangaza ngo N! Xau yasubizwaga mu rugo rwe mu butayu bwa Kalahari buri byumweru bitatu cyangwa bine kugira ngo atababazwa n’umuco .  Mu gihe mu mijyi, N! Xau yize kunywa inzoga n'itabi. <ref name="klemesrud" /> Uys yavuze ko yishyuye N! Xau $ 300 mu minsi 10 ya mbere yakoraga, ariko ko amafaranga bivugwa ko yatwawe n'umuyaga. <ref name="klemesrud" />  N! Xau yahise yishyurwa n'inka 12. <ref name="klemesrud" /> Mu 1985, Uys yavuze ko yohereje N! Xau $ 100 buri kwezi kuva yafata amashusho, N! Xau yakoresheje mu iduka ry’ubucuruzi ku bilometero 60 uvuye aho yahigaga; <ref name="klemesrud" /> Uys yavuze kandi ko hashyizweho konti y’amadolari 20.000 y’izina rya N! Xau. <ref name="klemesrud" />

== Controversies ==
''The Gods Must Be Crazy'' yakunze kunengwa kubera ko bigaragara ko ikomeje imyumvire ishingiye ku moko n'ivangura n'ivangura muri Afurika y'Epfo.  Muri Amerika, ngo iyi filime yatowe n’inama y’igihugu y’abavoka b’abirabura n’indi mitwe irwanya ivanguramoko ubwo yerekanaga mu nzu ya Street Street ya 68 mu mujyi wa New York. <ref name="klemesrud" />
